            <title>[HBASE-1118] Scanner setup takes too long</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-1118</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;posix4 and dj_ryan are on about scanner setups take too long.  Use case is fetch of a 100 - 1000 rows at a time.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
